ABOUT

$TRIPPE

In the heart of the $ZOGZ Kingdom, where frogs are known as Pepes once lived a plucky Pepe(Frog) named $TRIPPE, who aimed to conquer the territory and crown himself king after witnessing the malicious attitude of King PEPE. With relentless determination and acrobatic prowess, $TRIPPE outshone the king and his warriors ($DORKL, $RHC etc) in their own games, earning the respect of the kingdom. He became the legendary ruler proving that audacity knows no bounds and making the $ZOGZ KINGDOM GREAT AGAIN.

$TRIPPE’s unconventional and daring behavior, such as challenging the king and trying to establish himself as a leader in their territory, makes him THE TRIPPIEST $PEPE.
